PrecisAppointment of PHILIPPE BEAULNE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Senegal; ANDRÃ‰E COOLIGAN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Finland; DAVID DEVINE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Socialist Republic of Vietnam; NICOLE GILES as High Commissioner for Canada in the Co operative Republic of Guyana and as Plenipotentiary Representative of Canada to the Caribbean Community (CARICOM), and as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Suriname, with residence in Georgetown; LISA HELFAND as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Hungary; DEBORAH LYONS as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Afghanistan; JENNIFER MACINTYRE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Swiss Confederation; PETER MCGOVERN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Italian Republic and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the Food and Agriculture Organization, the World Food Programme, and the International Fund for Agricultural Development, as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of San Marino, with residence in Rome and as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Malta, with residence in Rome; ISABELLE POUPART as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe, in Vienna; NEIL REEDER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of the Philippines; and STUART SAVAGE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guatemala and as High Commissioner for Canada in Belize, with residence in Guatemala City.
